nodes.name: _getSettingVariables

determinePosition(address,address).details: Determine whether or not `_sender` is Advocate/Listener/Speaker of the Name/TAO

params._sender: The ETH address that to check

determinePosition(address,address).return: 1 if Advocate. 2 if Listener. 3 if Speaker

getChallengeStatus(bytes32,address).return: status of the challenge	1 = Can complete challenge	2 = Challenge not exist	3 = Sender is not the creator of the challenge	4 = Transaction is not in the allowed period of time	5 = Challenge has been completed	6 = Challenger has less Logos than current Advocate of TAO

getPositionById(address).return: the Advocate namethe Advocate ID of Name/TAOthe Listener namethe Listener ID of Name/TAOthe Speaker namethe Speaker ID of Name/TAO

getTAOAdvocateChallengeById(bytes32).details: Get TAOAdvocateChallenge info given an ID
getTAOAdvocateChallengeById(bytes32).return: the new Advocate ID in the challengethe ID of Name/TAOthe completion status of the challengethe created timestampthe lockedUntil timestamp (The deadline for current Advocate to respond)the completeBefore timestamp (The deadline for the challenger to respond and complete the challenge)

params._advocateId: The Advocate ID of the Name/TAO
params._listenerId: The Listener ID of the Name/TAO
params._speakerId: The Speaker ID of the Name/TAO

isExist(address).details: Check whether or not a Name/TAO ID exist in the list

nameIsAdvocate(address,address).details: Check whether or not _nameId is advocate of _id

params._nameId: The name ID to be checked

senderIsAdvocate(address,address).details: Check whether or not `_sender` eth address is Advocate of _id

senderIsAdvocateOfParent(address,address.details: Check whether or not `_sender` eth address is Advocate of Parent of _id

senderIsListener(address,address).details: Check whether or not `_sender` eth address is Listener of _id

senderIsPosition(address,address).details: Check whether or not eth address is either Advocate/Listener/Speaker of _id

senderIsSpeaker(address,address).details: Check whether or not `_sender` eth address is Speaker of _id

setAOSettingAddress(address).details: The AO sets AO Setting address

params._newAdvocateId: The new advocate ID to be set

params._newListenerId: The new listener ID to be set

setLogosAddress(address).details: The AO set the logosAddress Address

setNameAccountRecoveryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameAccountRecovery Address

setNameFactoryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameFactory Address

setSettingTAOId(address).details: The AO sets setting TAO ID

params._settingTAOId: The new setting TAO ID to set

params._newSpeakerId: The new speaker ID to be set

setTAOAncestryAddress(address).details: The AO set the TAOAncestry Address

setTAOFactoryAddress(address).details: The AO set the TAOFactory Address

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

challengeTAOAdvocate(address).notice: A Name challenges current TAO's Advocate to be its new Advocate

completeTAOAdvocateChallenge(bytes32).notice: Only owner of challenge can respond and complete of the challenge

getChallengeStatus(bytes32,address).notice: Get status of a TAOAdvocateChallenge given a `_challengeId` and a `_sender` eth address

parentReplaceChildAdvocate(address).notice: Only Advocate of Parent of `_taoId` can replace child `_taoId` 's Advocate with himself
